    {
      "id": "1b64750c-f3ba-8053-9a97-d0a757601170",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors use what is called Fair Capacitated Clustering on data from 14251 learners in K-12. Results show that 3 clusters appear for high-performing students:",
